sep.gaia.resources

Class DuplicateFreeQueue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.resources.DuplicateFreeQueue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the queues entries.

    public class DuplicateFreeQueue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a single-direction queue with unique entries (checked by equals()). Furthermore an priority can be assigned to each entry. The element with the highest priority will be returned first independent of its actual position. If priorities are equal, the element first inserted is returned. All methods in this class are designed for asynchronous access.
    Author:
    Matthias Fisch
